title: Pussy
description:
A bunch of pussy's get a pep talk!

Written by Katelyn Trela

Featuring Michael Delisle, Maya Deshmukh, Tessa Hersh, Tristan Griffin and Chrissy Shackelford, Willy Appelman, Brad Temple, Katelyn Trela, Ariel Karlin, Jasmine Pierce and Nick Ramirez.
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
